summary: A simple Preset featuring my newest character that I had made. I got bored of the standard Nord theme that I had been following for a while.
descriptionHtml:
Maella is a Nord character made to look like a alternate dark elf style character(prefer the Nord dialogue and passives), I had felt that a dark elf would be a step in a new direction for me and I wanted to step out of my comfort zone.

If you feel that your system can't run this ENB with enhanced textures and lighting mods I will list my personal system specs as of the time this is being made.

EVGA GeForce GTX 1060 6GB SSC ACX 3.0

i5 7600k 3.8GHz (Base clock)

Corsair Vengeance LPX 3,000MHz (downclocked to 2,400MHz due to mobo restrictions)

MSI B250 Gaming Pro Carbon motherboard

CRYORIG H7 CPU cooler

2TB 7,200RPM 6GB/s HDD (No SSD yet)



Mods I used:

SkyUI- https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3863

Rampage ENB- https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/67483/ + Parallax textures and texture overhauls and lighting

SKSE(Use installer or 7Zip)- http://skse.silverlock.org/

Bodyslide- https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49015/

UNP Blessed Body- https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37900/

HDT(For "immersion ")- https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53996/

XP32 Skeleton- https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26800/

Witcher 3 Eyes- https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/79622

Eyes Of Beauty- https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722

Maevan2's Eye Brows- https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72825/

Better Female Eyebrows- https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50302/

ApachiiSkyHair- https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/

Demonaic Textures UUNP (8K textures used for screenshots and gameplay)- https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70834/


I made this list for a fresh install if you are new or just restarting, I really hope you enjoy my content though the quality is questionable on some things.
After a long break I believe I may start making presets again and posting my characters to the nexus for everyone to enjoy.
author: CynicalAce
